l BAO measurements can be used as standard rulers if we\nassume wCDM type of models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2010 18:18:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2011 20:02:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Jan 2011 01:22:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
