nger-period systems\nindicate that the evolutionary models are broadly valid in the M~0.35-0.80 Msun\nregime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Nov 2010 21:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
